  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Topical menthol gels are classified 'topical analgesics' and are used to relieve aching and
      tenderness of muscles and joints. However, double-blind randomized controlled trials are
      lacking. Here the investigators examine - in a double-blind randomized controlled cross-over
      trial - the acute effect of topical menthol (Biofreeze) and placebo (gel with a menthol
      scent) on neck pain.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
