  <primary_outcome>
    <measure>Neck pain intensity (scale 0-10)</measure>
    <time_frame>before and 20 min after application</time_frame>
    <description>the participant rates pain intensity on a scale from 0-10 immediately before, and 0, 10, 20, 40 and 60 minutes after application of the gel. The primary efficacy endpoint is at 20 min</description>
